<figureCitation box="[334,433,1924,1949]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–10" captionStartId="3.[151,264,1946,1969]" captionTargetBox="[173,1420,202,1918]" captionTargetId="figure@3.[167,1431,193,1930]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 1–10. Riseveinus cervcornutus sp. nov.: 1. male habitus, dorsal view; 2. male habitus, lateral view; 3. male head and thorax, dorsal view; 4. male face; 5. male pygofer, lateral view; 6. male pygofer side, lateral view; 7. connective and style, ventral view; 8. aedeagal, ventral view; 9. aedeagal, lateral view; 10. subgenital plate, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2607074/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="260">Figs 1, 3</figureCitation>
